{"tid":1893100,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"稱美斯混蛋，伊巴教練：他比賽期間會休息","createTime":"2020-02-23T04:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T11:27:33.000Z","uid":4959,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"da8295da56fcac21f985fc552f6e56967e95cdcc","tid":1893100,"uid":4959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:20:14.000Z","msg":"在鬥巴塞賽前，伊巴主帥Jose Mendiliba語出驚人，稱美斯為「混蛋」：「我不認為美斯會在對我們時休息。他是個在比賽中休息的混蛋。他往往知道什麼時候要參與行動，什麼時候可以休息。要他比賽日休息坐在場邊，我想搞不好對他來說這樣才更累。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.goal.com/zh-hk/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E7%A8%B1-%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%AF-%E6%B7%B7%E8%9B%8B-%E4%BC%8A%E5%B7%B4-%E6%95%99%E7%B7%B4-%E4%BB%96-%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD-%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93-%E6%9C%83-%E4%BC%91%E6%81%AF/1abwju90chd319b0u5dnjdlg6?utm_source=whatsapp&amp;utm_medium=siteshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goal.com%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E7%25A8%25B1-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2596%25AF-%25E6%25B7%25B7%25E8%259B%258B-%25E4%25BC%258A%25E5%25B7%25B4-%25E6%2595%2599%25E7%25B7%25B4-%25E4%25BB%2596-%25E6%25AF%2594%25E8%25B3%25BD-%25E6%259C%259F%25E9%2596%2593-%25E6%259C%2583-%25E4%25BC%2591%25E6%2581%25AF%2F1abwju90chd319b0u5dnjdlg6%3Futm_source%3Dwhatsapp%26utm_medium%3Dsiteshare&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=f6cea27f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.goal.com/zh-hk/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E7%A8%B1-%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%AF-%E6%B7%B7%E8%9B%8B-%E4%BC%8A%E5%B7%B4-%E6%95%99%E7%B7%B4-%E4%BB%96-%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD-%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93-%E6%9C%83-%E4%BC%91%E6%81%AF/1abwju90chd319b0u5dnjdlg6?utm_source=whatsapp&amp;utm_medium=siteshare</a>"},{"pid":"446c7283c9d5aa5948673c8b941eafd3dd8d9c54","tid":1893100,"uid":29993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T06:11:37.000Z","msg":"散步帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895c2572c98d31656c9850ad30c0093bd2d4583f","tid":1893100,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-2